   310	            f"- Validation rows: `{report['summary']['validation_count']}`",
   311	            "",
   312	            "The smoke registers a concrete artifact against the SQLite schema from `REQ-020`, computes a SHA-256 hash from disk, records the producer operation, stores the artifact contract id and provenance in registry JSON, links evidence rows, graph edges, validation rows, and verifies the artifact-index view.",
   313	        ]
